body_html:
Heads up that there is now a TensorFlow kernel that wraps warp-ctc in the master branch of the warp-ctc repository: https://github.com/baidu-research/warp-ctc

(note that it too does not support proprocess_collapse_repeated=true or ctc_merge_repeated=false)
